headline: Why Alexandria Real Estate Stock Tumbled on Tuesday
summary: Although net income is usually not the key profitability metric for REITs, this one missed badly on the line item in its first quarter.  The company also sliced its revenue and profitability guidance for the full year.  Investors were bearish on the equity of Alexandria Real Estate Equities (NYSE: ARE) throughout Tuesday's trading session.
